s of Chinese officials and businesses for implementing a new national security law that would curtail the rights and freedoms of Hong Kong citizens.<br />\n<br />\nInter-agency discussions are ongoing and no decision has been made on whether or how to employ the sanctions, said the people, who spoke on condition of anonymity because the moves are still under consideration.<br />\n<br />\nMore information is available on the Bloomberg Terminal. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/amp/news/articles/2020-05-26/u-s-weighs-sanctions-on-chinese-officials-firms-over-hong-kong-kaobpsbv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2020-05-26%2Fu-s-weighs-sanctions-on-chinese-officials-firms-over-hong-kong-kaobpsbv&d=y71HX3BFsGTccDILyV%2F8U63e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=e3bd4ad7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/amp/news/articles/2020-05-26/u-s-weighs-sanctions-on-chinese-officials-firms-over-hong-kong-kaobpsbv</a>"},{"pid":"8e55d2d77be3b6373c1fca01a4bbebd0e6f1a39f","tid":2037001,"uid":95138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e1d4ed94e3be179a3005a77ab1efaa692466c672","tid":2037001,"uid":113724,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T19:51:55.000Z","msg":"係啦係啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T20:03:24.000Z","msg":"收返埋D晦氣說話啦 屌你老母"},{"pid":"27cb3d7be07d66604752de865200a698a02136ba","tid":2037001,"uid":270889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f2d40d5353ebb9d1098959737445f90c6c27b0a5","tid":2037001,"uid":3873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21317caa377c0d73a6cb42f1bdaefd4fd33685ee","tid":2037001,"uid":148053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2749f8fa4dd8c77143708748e4688de487e9c38e","tid":2037001,"uid":470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T19:53:18.000Z","msg":"郁港共果啲先 會唔會有效啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支共高官唔會用自己名去搞生意 制裁佢地到喉唔到